Advanced ChibiOS Project Template
===========
:Author:    Matthias Blaicher
:Email:     <matthias@blaicher.com>


== Intoduction
This project is meant to be a versatile framework to develop rich STM32
applications based on the ChibiOS RTOS.

It is specifically designed to run on the STM32P107 board by Olimex but will
also on othe hardware.

It specifically requires:
- Ethernet for communication
- SD Card for configuration saving